535
00:22:12,450 --> 00:22:13,560
I haven't won a single round.

536
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:15,400
I was about to ask you for more chips.

537
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,550
If you need more, ask them.

538
00:22:16,550 --> 00:22:18,030
How much longer are you playing?

539
00:22:18,030 --> 00:22:18,740
Are we leaving?

540
00:22:18,740 --> 00:22:20,670
The second venue is waiting for us.

541
00:22:20,690 --> 00:22:22,400
Is he a friend of yours?

542
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:24,010
Yes, let me introduce.

543
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:26,130
Ye Siyuan, Mr. Ye.

544
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:28,230
His uncle is Ye Tianyou.

545
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:32,360
This is Mr. Luo, a big shot in Hanzhou.

546
00:22:33,310 --> 00:22:34,240
Nice to meet you.

547
00:22:34,590 --> 00:22:35,150
Mr. Luo.

548
00:22:36,470 --> 00:22:37,300
Can we go now?

549
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:38,480
Last five rounds.

550
00:22:38,550 --> 00:22:39,470
Mr. Ye, try a couple of rounds.

551
00:22:39,470 --> 00:22:40,400
I don't know how.

552
00:22:40,730 --> 00:22:41,610
It's super easy.

553
00:22:41,610 --> 00:22:42,570
You'll get it just by watching.

554
00:22:42,570 --> 00:22:44,150
Here, five for Mr. Ye.

555
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:50,240
Place your bets. Players bet, please.

556
00:22:50,430 --> 00:22:51,610
Is there no rule

557
00:22:51,890 --> 00:22:53,070
to how your chips are handled?

558
00:22:53,070 --> 00:22:54,270
We make our own rules.

559
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:58,370
Don't move.

560
00:23:07,060 --> 00:23:08,060
I've got you beat.

561
00:23:08,370 --> 00:23:09,230
Give me the money!

562
00:23:09,230 --> 00:23:10,120
That's a win?

563
00:23:10,150 --> 00:23:10,870
We won.

564
00:23:10,900 --> 00:23:12,760
Easy, right? Play another round?

565
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:16,040
This is too boring.

566
00:23:16,970 --> 00:23:18,970
Take this for tea money for the boys.

567
00:23:21,840 --> 00:23:22,470
Mr. Luo.

568
00:23:23,040 --> 00:23:24,440
Let me make a suggestion.

569
00:23:24,550 --> 00:23:26,680
The dealer here is too... well,

