00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:30,500
how about getting
a pretty female dealer next time?

571
00:23:32,550 --> 00:23:33,110
Well...

572
00:23:36,810 --> 00:23:37,940
That's a good point.

573
00:23:41,420 --> 00:23:42,270
Come on.

574
00:23:42,900 --> 00:23:44,830
Deal the cards and let's continue.

575
00:23:49,590 --> 00:23:52,520
These mobile gambling operations
are hard to catch.

576
00:23:53,780 --> 00:23:54,860
Figure out

577
00:23:54,890 --> 00:23:56,890
how to get us
inside to investigate.

578
00:23:59,790 --> 00:24:01,210
This Ye Siyuan

579
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:03,610
is Ye Tianyou's nephew

580
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:06,640
and they're as close as father and son.

581
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:09,530
Ye Siyuan causes no major troubles

582
00:24:09,530 --> 00:24:10,930
but plenty of minor ones.

583
00:24:11,290 --> 00:24:12,800
Everyone

584
00:24:12,980 --> 00:24:14,510
respects Ye Tianyou enough

585
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:16,690
to give him some leeway.

586
00:24:16,750 --> 00:24:19,540
That means if we want to
keep Ye Tianyou stable,

587
00:24:20,210 --> 00:24:22,040
this man is the key person.

588
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,510
We can try this approach.

589
00:24:27,890 --> 00:24:29,550
Mr. Wang, let me report to you.

590
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:33,080
After interacting
with this person, I found

591
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:34,740
he's arrogant

592
00:24:35,230 --> 00:24:36,890
and completely unrealistic.

593
00:24:37,490 --> 00:24:39,910
It's impossible to get along with him.

594
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:42,160
Even if you can't get along with him,

595
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:43,020
you must try,

596
00:24:43,560 --> 00:24:46,750
and become good friends, even brothers.

597
00:24:48,250 --> 00:24:51,510
It's impossible to become brothers
with someone like him.

598
00:25:00,370 --> 00:25:01,150
Luo.

599
00:25:01,410 --> 00:25:02,140
Mr. Wang.

600
00:25:02,650 --> 00:25:05,340
With Ye Siyuan,
you can play the long game.

601
00:25:06,360 --> 00:25:07,750
The most important thing now

602
00:25:07,750 --> 00:25:09,820
is to solve Longwan's problem first.

603
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:11,700
Understood, Mr. Wang.

604
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:18,700
Mr. Wang, your ginseng...

605
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,440
That one in the middle

606
00:25:29,460 --> 00:25:30,520
is Zhao Peng's son.

607
00:25:41,060 --> 00:25:42,340
You're doing well.

608
00:25:42,790 --> 00:25:45,460
[Zhao Wenxuan, son of Zhao Peng]

609
00:25:45,460 --> 00:25:46,790
So you're Zhao Wenxuan?

610
00:25:47,420 --> 00:25:48,140
Who are you?

611
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:52,270
Hurry up.

612
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:09,790
[Longwan Farming Company]

613
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:12,810
Bo.

614
00:26:13,810 --> 00:26:15,840
I've taken care of everything.

615
00:26:15,990 --> 00:26:18,710
So can we settle

616
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:20,060
our debt now?

617
00:26:20,930 --> 00:26:23,030
That depends on how you perform next.

618
00:26:26,140 --> 00:26:27,670
What else do you need me to do?

619
00:26:27,670 --> 00:26:29,600
Longwan refuses to lease the land.

620
00:26:29,820 --> 00:26:31,770
Many people must be unhappy about it.

621
00:26:31,770 --> 00:26:32,900
Go talk to them.

622
00:26:37,300 --> 00:26:39,130
This... this matter...

623
00:26:39,810 --> 00:26:41,200
No, no, this...

624
00:26:41,890 --> 00:26:43,030
If my brother finds out,

625
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:44,640
he'll kill me.

626
00:26:44,740 --> 00:26:46,340
If you settle the land issue,

627
00:26:46,970 --> 00:26:48,630
forget about your small debt.

628
00:26:49,170 --> 00:26:51,100
I'll make sure you live in a mansion

629
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:52,770
and drink fine champagne.

630
00:27:06,030 --> 00:27:06,680
Jiangyong.

631
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:07,430
What's wrong?

632
00:27:07,430 --> 00:27:08,480
Many of our chicken

633
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:09,460
have died.

634
00:27:09,530 --> 00:27:10,640
The rest look sick.

635
00:27:10,660 --> 00:27:11,660
What should we do?

636
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,530
Is this person

637
00:27:27,510 --> 00:27:28,790
Zhao Peng's son?

638
00:27:35,350 --> 00:27:36,200
That's right.

639
00:27:36,450 --> 00:27:37,330
Yes, it's him.

640
00:27:37,360 --> 00:27:38,030
It's him.

641
00:27:38,190 --> 00:27:39,570
This is so despicable.

642
00:27:40,060 --> 00:27:40,870
Call the police.

643
00:27:40,870 --> 00:27:41,880
Don't call the police yet.

644
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:42,560
I want to

645
00:27:42,850 --> 00:27:44,180
settle this privately.

646
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,560
Let's call the police.

647
00:27:46,830 --> 00:27:49,160
It's one thing that Zhao Peng
won't cooperate with us,

648
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,600
but he's also helping Ma Jin against us.

649
00:27:50,600 --> 00:27:53,240
This is exactly when we need to stay calm.

650
00:27:53,370 --> 00:27:55,470
If you don't call the police,
at least make him pay for damages.

651
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:57,200
How can they bully us like this?

652
00:27:57,850 --> 00:27:58,890
Let's go to Zhao Peng.

653
00:27:58,890 --> 00:28:00,820
We'll settle all accounts at once.

654
00:28:00,840 --> 00:28:01,920
This is too much.

655
00:28:13,270 --> 00:28:14,070
Peng!

656
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:15,160
Peng.

657
00:28:15,650 --> 00:28:16,910
Something terrible happened!

658
00:28:16,910 --> 00:28:18,440
Someone poisoned Longwan.

659
00:28:19,890 --> 00:28:21,530
It's probably Luo Bo and his people.

660
00:28:21,530 --> 00:28:22,610
Wenxuan did it.

661
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:23,720
Who?

662
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:25,070
Wenxuan?

663
00:28:25,720 --> 00:28:26,510
Are you serious?

664
00:28:26,510 --> 00:28:28,920
It's true. Longwan checked
the security footage.

665
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:29,790
Where is Wenxuan?

666
00:28:29,790 --> 00:28:30,810
He's at Longwan.

667
00:28:32,510 --> 00:28:33,310
Get everyone.

668
00:28:36,350 --> 00:28:37,310
Where's my son?

669
00:28:37,330 --> 00:28:38,400
Hand over my son!

670
00:28:38,430 --> 00:28:39,270
Zhao Peng,

671
00:28:39,290 --> 00:28:40,560
don't you know what terrible thing

672
00:28:40,560 --> 00:28:41,480
your son has done?

673
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:42,440
So what if I know?

674
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:43,400
All I know now is

675
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:44,600
you've locked him up!

676
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:45,360
Yes!

677
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:47,720
We locked him up! Your son broke the law!

678
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:48,510
So what if he broke the law?

679
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:49,440
Breaking the law means he gets locked up!

680
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,680
The police handle lawbreakers,

681
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,990
not you people!

682
00:28:52,020 --> 00:28:52,880
I'm telling you,

683
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:54,070
if you don't release my son today,

684
00:28:54,070 --> 00:28:57,070
I'll tear down your ancestral hall,
believe it or not.

685
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,420
Calm down, Jiangyong.

686
00:29:05,320 --> 00:29:06,190
Stop!

687
00:29:06,560 --> 00:29:07,620
Everyone stop now!

688
00:29:08,430 --> 00:29:09,290
Longwan people,

689
00:29:09,290 --> 00:29:10,490
step back, all of you.

690
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:16,550
Want to end up at the police station?

691
00:29:20,180 --> 00:29:21,240
Your son is inside.

692
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:23,010
Let's go in and talk.

693
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:28,000
Leave it to me, okay?

694
00:29:28,960 --> 00:29:29,770
Wait here.

695
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,200
I'll kill you!

696
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:48,770
I'll beat you to death,

697
00:29:48,770 --> 00:29:49,890
you worthless thing!

698
00:29:49,890 --> 00:29:51,680
Do you know what trouble you've caused?

699
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:52,880
Do you have any idea

700
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:54,410
how much trouble you're in?

701
00:29:56,030 --> 00:29:56,720
Come on.

702
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:58,150
You useless thing!

703
00:29:58,350 --> 00:29:59,880
Why don't you hear what he has to say?

704
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:00,920
What does he have to say?

705
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,580
What do you want to say? Speak.

706
00:30:04,120 --> 00:30:05,520
It was Luo Bo and his gang.

707
00:30:05,770 --> 00:30:07,300
They tied me up in their car.

708
00:30:07,900 --> 00:30:10,500
They forced me
to poison Longwan's reservoir.

709
00:30:11,290 --> 00:30:13,220
Otherwise, they threatened
to come after us.

710
00:30:13,220 --> 00:30:13,940
Luo Bo?

711
00:30:14,930 --> 00:30:16,130
So it's not his fault.

712
00:30:16,850 --> 00:30:18,380
Luo Bo and his people did it.

713
00:30:19,070 --> 00:30:20,090
He's still in school.

714
00:30:20,090 --> 00:30:21,020
If I really call the police,

715
00:30:21,020 --> 00:30:22,130
it'll stay on his record for life.

716
00:30:22,130 --> 00:30:22,860
Not worth it.

717
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,000
Thanks.

718
00:30:27,790 --> 00:30:29,250
Whatever losses you have,

719
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:31,000
I'll pay for everything.

720
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:34,260
Whether you pay or not,
the chicken farm is already ruined.

721
00:30:35,030 --> 00:30:36,090
What else do you want?

722
00:30:36,090 --> 00:30:37,350
I don't want anything.

723
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,560
I just want to ask you—

724
00:30:38,560 --> 00:30:39,690
are you going to keep

725
00:30:39,810 --> 00:30:41,470
working with Ma Jin and Luo Bo?

726
00:30:42,150 --> 00:30:42,870
Peng,

727
00:30:43,770 --> 00:30:46,110
your Zhao Village is in the same situation
as our Longwan now.

728
00:30:46,110 --> 00:30:47,170
How to move forward

729
00:30:47,990 --> 00:30:50,520
is something
you need to figure out yourself.

730
00:30:56,410 --> 00:30:58,560
[Food and Drug Supervision]

731
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,280
We've received reports from the public

732
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:01,600
that Longwan Farming Company

733
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:02,680
has violated

734
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:04,690
food safety regulations during production.

735
00:31:04,690 --> 00:31:06,300
After our investigation,

736
00:31:06,430 --> 00:31:07,630
we confirm these allegations are true.

737
00:31:07,630 --> 00:31:07,920
[Seal of the Xingang District
Food and Drug Administration]

738
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:10,000
Longwan Farming Company is hereby ordered

739
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,110
to suspend operations

740
00:31:11,110 --> 00:31:12,490
for rectification, effective immediately.

741
00:31:12,490 --> 00:31:15,130
[Longwan Farming Company]

742
00:31:15,890 --> 00:31:16,330
Wait.

743
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:18,690
How can you just shut us down like this?

744
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:20,500
You're cutting off our livelihood.

745
00:31:20,500 --> 00:31:21,900
Are you trying to kill us?

746
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:23,630
This is too much!

747
00:31:23,860 --> 00:31:25,260
I won't sign
no matter how much they offer.

748
00:31:25,260 --> 00:31:26,460
Let's fight them now.

749
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:27,370
Tianye.

750
00:31:27,390 --> 00:31:29,140
What do you say? We'll follow you.

751
00:31:29,140 --> 00:31:29,860
I think

752
00:31:30,070 --> 00:31:31,880
as long as we stand together,
we fear nothing.

753
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:32,510
Right?

754
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:33,310
Yes!

755
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:35,460
Alright.

756
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:36,930
Behaving like this

757
00:31:36,930 --> 00:31:38,520
won't solve anything.

758
00:31:39,610 --> 00:31:41,210
Everyone, please disperse.

759
00:31:50,130 --> 00:31:53,160
[Memorial Tablet
of My Late Husband, Liu Guoqiang]

760
00:32:05,210 --> 00:32:05,860
Tianye.

761
00:32:06,620 --> 00:32:08,510
What should we do next?

762
00:32:10,450 --> 00:32:12,580
I want to cooperate with Zhao Village.

763
00:32:17,310 --> 00:32:19,840
Just mentioning Zhao Village
makes me upset.

764
00:32:24,250 --> 00:32:25,050
I'm upset too.

765
00:32:26,450 --> 00:32:27,540
Sometimes I dream

766
00:32:30,290 --> 00:32:32,440
about those balls of fire.

767
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:35,270
But

768
00:32:37,190 --> 00:32:39,850
I don't want Longwan
to end with our generation.

769
00:32:41,330 --> 00:32:42,800
If we don't work together,

770
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:46,130
Ma Jin might take over everything.

771
00:32:46,980 --> 00:32:48,710
Zhao Peng isn't stupid either.

772
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:50,660
I think

773
00:32:51,260 --> 00:32:52,390
we can pull this off.

774
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:56,200
You're in charge anyway,

775
00:32:57,230 --> 00:32:58,760
so do what you think is best.

776
00:33:08,130 --> 00:33:09,100
Chief Huang.

777
00:33:09,890 --> 00:33:10,440
I know.

778
00:33:10,470 --> 00:33:11,200
Yes.

779
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:11,730
Right.

780
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:13,800
I understand.

781
00:33:14,830 --> 00:33:15,270
Okay.

782
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,310
So, recently in Longwan

783
00:33:18,310 --> 00:33:20,370
there have been quite a few problems.

784
00:33:20,620 --> 00:33:23,220
If we need help later,
I hope you can lend a hand.

785
00:33:23,890 --> 00:33:24,440
Alright.

786
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:25,260
Bye.

787
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:27,530
Tianye,

788
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:30,430
if anything happens, just call the police.

789
00:33:30,430 --> 00:33:31,510
I've already put in a good word.

790
00:33:31,510 --> 00:33:33,640
The station chief
in this area is my friend.

791
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:34,900
I just didn't want to cause trouble.

792
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:36,560
And Wenxuan is still so young.

793
00:33:37,070 --> 00:33:39,000
What's the trouble
with calling the police?

794
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:39,480
Right?

795
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,370
We know how to
handle these things properly.

796
00:33:41,370 --> 00:33:43,440
Alright, then I'll come to you
if anything comes up, okay?

797
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:45,300
Sure, you can report to me as well.

798
00:33:47,050 --> 00:33:50,050
It's better to resolve conflicts
than to create them.

799
00:33:50,980 --> 00:33:52,150
Do you all remember?

800
00:33:53,410 --> 00:33:55,510
This is where it happened back then.

801
00:33:57,800 --> 00:33:59,410
If I could go back,

802
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:03,330
I would have stopped them no matter what.

803
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:08,080
[Longwan; 1990]

804
00:34:08,670 --> 00:34:09,440
Alright.

805
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:11,510
Feng.

806
00:34:11,510 --> 00:34:11,699
Learn more from Tianye.

807
00:34:11,699 --> 00:34:13,030
[Qin Lizhi, Qin Feng's father]

808
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:14,070
Stop causing trouble all the time.

809
00:34:14,070 --> 00:34:14,670
All right.

810
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:15,920
I know, Dad.

811
00:34:16,070 --> 00:34:17,030
You little rascal.

812
00:34:17,030 --> 00:34:18,230
Don't worry, Mr. Qin,

813
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:19,400
I'll keep an eye on Feng.

814
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:20,550
I'm here too.

815
00:34:20,550 --> 00:34:21,510
I'll help you watch over him as well.

816
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:23,310
Right. My Yan will help you, too.

817
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:24,000
Remember.

818
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:25,280
Don't make trouble.

819
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:26,320
Okay.

820
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,030
Be good.

821
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,150
We should head back now,

822
00:34:30,150 --> 00:34:30,920
Go back.

823
00:34:31,429 --> 00:34:32,380
Be careful.

824
00:34:32,409 --> 00:34:33,090
Goodbye.

825
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:33,760
Dad.

826
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:34,530
I'm leaving.

827
00:34:53,330 --> 00:34:54,820
-Dad!
-Mom!

828
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:54,800
Excuse me.

829
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,070
Make way, please.

830
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:03,880
[Police Line]

831
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:04,730
Someone died. Look.

832
00:36:04,730 --> 00:36:05,130
[Zhao the Eldest,
Zhao Village's fishing bully]

833
00:36:05,130 --> 00:36:05,940
Several.

834
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,240
[Police Line]

835
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:09,250
Zhao the Eldest,

836
00:36:09,650 --> 00:36:10,860
did you do this?

837
00:36:11,110 --> 00:36:12,760
Was it you?

838
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:13,630
Jiangyong!

839
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,360
Be responsible for what you say.

840
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:16,070
What do you mean I did it?

841
00:36:16,070 --> 00:36:18,030
I just got here. What could I have done?

842
00:36:18,030 --> 00:36:18,760
Let go of me!

843
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:19,400
One.

844
00:36:19,710 --> 00:36:20,710
Jiangyong, let go.

845
00:36:20,710 --> 00:36:21,760
Listen to me!

846
00:36:22,340 --> 00:36:22,470
Jiangyong, please listen to me.

847
00:36:22,470 --> 00:36:25,690
[Police Line]

848
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:33,070
I've always said only people
from Zhao Village can fish here,

849
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:36,320
but some people just wouldn't listen.

850
00:36:37,490 --> 00:36:38,550
They had it coming.

851
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:41,860
Mom,

852
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:44,200
don't overthink it.

853
00:36:51,430 --> 00:36:53,270
All these years,

854
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,760
I've nagged about this,

855
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:55,960
nagged about that,

856
00:36:56,840 --> 00:36:58,190
talked so much,

857
00:36:58,190 --> 00:37:00,520
and I don't know if you've been listening.

858
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:02,240
I don't mean anything else.

859
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:05,150
I just hope you all can live good lives.

860
00:37:05,770 --> 00:37:06,550
We've listened.

861
00:37:06,550 --> 00:37:08,110
We've listened to everything you said.

862
00:37:08,110 --> 00:37:10,310
Did you hear Madam Wen? Live a good life.

863
00:37:10,510 --> 00:37:12,770
We've all taken it in, see?
Everyone has.

864
00:37:13,130 --> 00:37:15,770
Alright, the wind is too strong.
Let's go back first.

865
00:37:15,770 --> 00:37:16,590
Let's go, Tianye.

866
00:37:16,590 --> 00:37:18,450
You go first. I'll sit for a while.

867
00:37:19,430 --> 00:37:20,740
Don't sit here too long.

868
00:37:20,740 --> 00:37:22,380
You might catch a cold.

869
00:37:27,840 --> 00:37:28,440
Tianye.

870
00:37:29,030 --> 00:37:30,730
Why did you have me put on

871
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:31,850
this show today?

872
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:34,250
Ma Jin and Luo Bo

873
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:36,190
have stood unshaken
in Hanzhou for so many years.

874
00:37:36,190 --> 00:37:37,920
There must be internal issues.

875
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:39,210
So I was thinking

876
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:40,000
that you

877
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:42,360
should infiltrate their organization.

878
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,150
Alright.

879
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,680
I'll do whatever you say.

880
00:37:46,630 --> 00:37:47,630
Can you handle it?

881
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:48,800
It's fine, Tianye.

882
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:49,330
I'm fine.

883
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:51,400
When dealing with someone like Luo Bo,

884
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:53,550
you need to be careful with boundaries.

885
00:37:53,550 --> 00:37:54,110
I know.

886
00:37:54,710 --> 00:37:56,250
They just want to use me

887
00:37:56,590 --> 00:37:58,120
and make me betray Longwan.

888
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,170
So what should I do next?

889
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:03,550
You...

890
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:07,670
First, you need to prove
your loyalty to them.

891
00:38:07,670 --> 00:38:09,530
So he and Ma Jin can trust you.

892
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:12,320
Then we can help your third brother
take him down.

893
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,280
But...

894
00:38:14,390 --> 00:38:16,070
I want to use Luo Bo's help

895
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:19,800
to bring Zhao Village to our side.

896
00:38:22,710 --> 00:38:23,320
How?

897
00:38:24,150 --> 00:38:25,760
Zhao Peng's son, Zhao Wenxuan.

898
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:26,960
We'll start with him.

899
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:30,320
What does he have to do with this?

900
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,040
You'll

901
00:38:31,150 --> 00:38:33,230
tell Luo Bo you've come up with an idea.

902
00:38:33,230 --> 00:38:34,200
Get Zhao Wenxuan

903
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:36,450
to poison our farm.

904
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:44,230
Zhao Peng loves his son
more than anything.

905
00:38:44,230 --> 00:38:46,000
Would he actually let his son
fall into Longwan's hands?

906
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:48,150
Their whole village
will deliberately come make trouble.

907
00:38:48,150 --> 00:38:51,150
That will prove the two villages
can't work together.

908
00:38:53,150 --> 00:38:55,960
Isn't that too high a price to pay
for this gesture of loyalty?

909
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:56,760
Is it worth it?

910
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:57,640
It's worth it.

911
00:38:58,230 --> 00:38:58,900
This way,

912
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:01,070
Luo Bo will think
he's cut off our livelihood.

913
00:39:01,070 --> 00:39:02,360
But he would never expect

914
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:04,630
that I'll eventually return Zhao Wenxuan.

915
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:06,670
I not only want you
to gain Luo Bo's trust,

916
00:39:06,670 --> 00:39:07,740
but also to bring me

917
00:39:08,030 --> 00:39:09,160
closer to Zhao Peng.

918
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:11,480
Tianye.

919
00:39:14,670 --> 00:39:15,880
I said what we planned.

920
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:16,110
[House of Benevolence]

921
00:39:16,110 --> 00:39:18,770
Luo Bo did force
Zhao Wenxuan to poison our farm.

922
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:24,970
I want to report something.

923
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:27,240
Longwan Farming Company

924
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:29,180
has major food safety issues

925
00:39:29,670 --> 00:39:31,870
that must be thoroughly investigated.

926
00:39:32,710 --> 00:39:33,150
Yes.

927
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:36,260
Well,

928
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:37,440
Tianye,

929
00:39:38,510 --> 00:39:39,310
aren't you...

930
00:39:40,710 --> 00:39:41,840
Being too ruthless?

931
00:39:43,230 --> 00:39:44,830
Without a point of no return,

932
00:39:45,030 --> 00:39:46,160
people will never truly unite.
